id="iv.iii.v.iii-p72.1"></span>Cutts, Edw. L</span>. *Constantine the
Great, the union of the State and the Church*. London and New York,
1881. 12o, XIV. 422 pp. For general, not especially scholarly use.

<span id="iv.iii.v.iii-p73"></span><span class="c11"><span
id="iv.iii.v.iii-p73.1"></span>Dalhus</span>. *Dissertatio de baptismo
Constantini Magni*. Hafniæ, 1696 (1698, Vogt.).

<span id="iv.iii.v.iii-p74"></span><span class="c11"><span
id="iv.iii.v.iii-p74.1"></span>Demetriades, Kalliop</span>. *Die
christliche Regierung und Orthodoxie Kaiser Constantin d. Grossen, eine
histor. Studie*. München, 1878. 8o, IV. 47 pp.

<span id="iv.iii.v.iii-p75"></span><span class="c11"><span
id="iv.iii.v.iii-p75.1"></span>Dieze, Joh. Andr</span>. *Dissertatio de
