<span id="iv.iii.v.iii-p121"></span><span id="page_460">p. 460</span>
<span id="iv.iii.v.iii-Page_460"></span><span class="c11"><span
id="iv.iii.v.iii-p121.1"></span>Harduin, J</span>. *Chronologia sæculi
Constantiniani ex solis numis antiquis*. In his *Op. sel*. p. 442–.

<span id="iv.iii.v.iii-p122"></span><span class="c11"><span
id="iv.iii.v.iii-p122.1"></span>Hartmann, J. A</span>. *Dissertatio
historica de Helena, Constantini Magni matre*. Marb. 1723. 4o.

<span id="iv.iii.v.iii-p123"></span><span class="c11"><span
id="iv.iii.v.iii-p123.1"></span>Hauck, A</span>. *Zur donatio
Constantini*. In Ztschr. f. kirchl. Wissensch. u. kirchl. Leben (1888),
201–207.

<span id="iv.iii.v.iii-p124"></span><span class="c11"><span
id="iv.iii.v.iii-p124.1"></span>Hebenstreit, G. E</span>. (=Hofmann, C.
