sepulchro*. Lipsiæ, 1759, 4o, 48 pp.

<span id="iv.iii.v.iii-p133"></span><span class="c11"><span
id="iv.iii.v.iii-p133.1"></span>Hojer, J. C</span>. *Quæ Constantino
Magno favoris in Christian. fuerunt caussæ*. Jenæ, 1758, 16 pp.

<span id="iv.iii.v.iii-p134"></span><span class="c11"><span
id="iv.iii.v.iii-p134.1"></span>Haute, Theodorus van der</span>. *Oratio
