<span id="iv.iii.v.iii-p143"></span>“<span class="c13"><span
id="iv.iii.v.iii-p143.1"></span>Janus</span>.” *Der Pabst und das
Concil*. Leipzig, 1869. 8o, xix, 451 pp.

<span id="iv.iii.v.iii-p144"></span><span class="c11"><span
id="iv.iii.v.iii-p144.1"></span>Jeep, Ludw</span>. *Zur Gesch.
Constantins*. Festschrift f. E. Curtius. (Berlin, 1884. 8o.) p. 79.

<span id="iv.iii.v.iii-p145"></span>*Journal des Sçavants*. (1774), p.
451–459. Review and analysis of Du Voisin.

<span id="iv.iii.v.iii-p146"></span><span class="c11"><span
id="iv.iii.v.iii-p146.1"></span>Kaufmann, Georg</span>. *Eine neue
Theorie über die Entstehung u. Tendenz der angeblichen Schenkung
Constantins*. In Allgem. Zeitung (1884), 194–196, 211–212. Valuable.
Weiland, p. 146–147.

<span id="iv.iii.v.iii-p147"></span><span class="c11"><span
id="iv.iii.v.iii-p147.1"></span>Kedd, Jod</span>. *Constantinus Magnus
