<span id="iv.iii.v.iii-p290"></span><span class="c11"><span
id="iv.iii.v.iii-p290.1"></span>Note 1.</span>–The number of works which
have suggested themselves as really necessary to complete a working list
for the student of Constantine is very great. Some works like <span
class="c13"><span id="iv.iii.v.iii-p290.2"></span>Hefele’s</span>
